# Diabetes Diagnostic & Risk Portal

This project in an AI-Powered diagnostic tool.It uses Machine Learning to provide three types of analysis:

1.** Binary Classification :** Predicts if a patient is Diabetic or not.
2.** Multiclass Classification:** Predicts the stage /grade of diabetes.
3.** Regression:** Predicts the overall Diabetes Risk Score.

## Tech Stack:
-Python ,Scikit-Learn,Streamlit,Joblib.

## How to run:

1.Install requirements : 'pip install -r requirements.txt'
2.Run the app:'streamlit run app.py'